'''''Asteropeia micraster''''' is a species of [[plant]] in the [[Asteropeiaceae]] family. It is [[Endemism|endemic]] to [[Madagascar]]. [[Category:Flora of Madagascar]] Its natural [[habitat]] is sandy shores. It is threatened by [[habitat loss]]. 

